"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwebsite=self.webpackChunkwebsite||[]).push([[1477],{10:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"Linux Talk","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/Linux Talk","source":"@site/blog/2024-04-19-linux-talk/index.md","title":"Linux Talk","description":"Linux Talk: Unveiling the Power of Open Source","date":"2024-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"April 19, 2024","tags":[{"label":"kuosc","permalink":"/blog/tags/kuosc"},{"label":"event","permalink":"/blog/tags/event"},{"label":"linux","permalink":"/blog/tags/linux"}],"readingTime":1.64,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Shriharsh Acharya","title":"General Member, KUOSC","url":"https://github.com/shri-acha","imageURL":"https://github.com/shri-acha.png","key":"irhs0"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"Linux Talk","title":"Linux Talk","authors":["irhs0"],"tags":["kuosc","event","linux"]},"nextItem":{"title":"Training at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home","permalink":"/blog/2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home"}},"content":"## Linux Talk: Unveiling the Power of Open Source\\n\\n<hr/>\\n<img\\nsrc={require(\'./img/linux_talk_01.jpg\').default}\\nalt=\\"penguin_holding_linux_talk\\"\\nheight=\\"50%\\" \\nwidth=\\"100%\\"\\n/>\\n\\n<hr/>\\n\\nOn April 19th,Linux talk a yearly event hosted by KUCC and KUOSC was held that offered a comprehensive exploration of open-source software and its underlying principles. The session delved into the collaborative nature of open-source development, where source code is freely available for inspection, modification, and contribution. This transparency fosters a unique environment that prioritizes innovation and community-driven problem-solving.Not only that but Linux talk but it also marked the inauguration of GNOME Nepal, a chapter dedicated to the popular open-source desktop environment.\\n\\nThe Linux talk itself delved into the collaborative nature of open-source development, where source code is freely available for inspection, modification, and contribution. This transparency fosters a unique environment that prioritizes innovation and community-driven problem-solving. The session explored the advantages of open-source software in detail, highlighting its potential for rapid advancement and user empowerment through accessible source code.\\n\\nA particularly engaging element of the event was a Kahoot session. This interactive quiz, employing a gamified approach, served as a fun and effective way to reinforce the key concepts presented during the talk. The competitive spirit fostered a sense of camaradarie amongst the attendees, further strengthening the connections made throughout the evening.\\n\\nFollowing the Linux talk, the stage was set for a special announcement \u2013 the official inauguration of GNOME Nepal. This new chapter promises to be a valuable resource for enthusiasts of the GNOME desktop environment, providing a platform for collaboration, learning, and promoting the adoption of open-source software in Nepal.\\n\\nThe combined event proved to be a rewarding experience. It not only offered a comprehensive understanding of open-source software and the benefits of the GNOME desktop environment but also fostered a sense of connection within the vibrant open-source community. The event\'s combination of informative content, interactive elements, and opportunities for networking solidified the value proposition of open-source software and its potential to drive innovation and collaboration in Nepal."},{"id":"2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home","source":"@site/blog/2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home/index.md","title":"Training at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home","description":"Training","date":"2024-02-21T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"February 21, 2024","tags":[{"label":"kuosc","permalink":"/blog/tags/kuosc"},{"label":"HeNN","permalink":"/blog/tags/he-nn"},{"label":"LTSP","permalink":"/blog/tags/ltsp"},{"label":"Training","permalink":"/blog/tags/training"}],"readingTime":0.8,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Aadarsha Dhakal","title":"Coordinator, KUOSC","url":"https://github.com/aadarshadhakalg","imageURL":"https://github.com/aadarshadhakalg.png","key":"aadarshadhakalg"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home","title":"Training at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home","authors":["aadarshadhakalg"],"tags":["kuosc","HeNN","LTSP","Training"]},"prevItem":{"title":"Linux Talk","permalink":"/blog/Linux Talk"},"nextItem":{"title":"Launch of the KUOSC Website","permalink":"/blog/websitelaunch"}},"content":"![Training](./training.jpg)\\n\\nVolunteers from Kathmandu University Open Source Community (KUOSC) in collaboration with Help Nepal Network Nepal (HeNN) conducted a training session for children at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home. The session focused on equipping the children with essential computer skills and fostering responsible internet usage.\\n\\nThe training aimed to familiarize the children with their newly upgraded computer lab. Volunteers guided them on navigating educational websites like E-Paathsala, E-paath, Maths and Science Quiz, and Hamro Ramailo Kathaharu offered by OLE Nepal. These platforms provide access to a wealth of learning materials, enhancing the children\'s educational opportunities.\\n\\nFurthermore, the volunteers emphasized internet safety, educating the children on responsible online behavior and navigating the digital world with caution.\\n\\n**Volunteers:**\\n- Aadarsha Dhakal\\n- Ayush Paudel\\n- Jamyang Gelek Gurung\\n\\n**From HeNN Nepal:**\\n- Merisha Kafle\\n- Anil Kumar Shrestha\\n\\n\\nThis collaborative effort empowers the children at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home with valuable technological skills and fosters responsible digital citizenship, paving the way for a brighter future."},{"id":"websitelaunch","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/websitelaunch","source":"@site/blog/2023-08-28-websitelaunch/index.md","title":"Launch of the KUOSC Website","description":"KUOSC Banner","date":"2023-08-28T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"August 28, 2023","tags":[{"label":"kuosc","permalink":"/blog/tags/kuosc"},{"label":"website","permalink":"/blog/tags/website"},{"label":"launch","permalink":"/blog/tags/launch"}],"readingTime":0.91,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Aadarsha Dhakal","title":"Coordinator, KUOSC","url":"https://github.com/aadarshadhakalg","imageURL":"https://github.com/aadarshadhakalg.png","key":"aadarshadhakalg"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"websitelaunch","title":"Launch of the KUOSC Website","authors":["aadarshadhakalg"],"tags":["kuosc","website","launch"]},"prevItem":{"title":"Training at Dhulikhel Children\'s Home","permalink":"/blog/2024-02-21-training-at-dhulikhel-childrens-home"}},"content":"![KUOSC Banner](./kuosc-plain-banner.jpeg)\\n\\nIntroducing the New KUOSC Website: Unveiling a Hub of Open Source Activities!\\n\\nThe Kathmandu University Open Source Community (KUOSC) proudly presents its brand-new website! Loaded with features and insights, this platform is set to become the go-to destination for all things related to open source.\\n\\n## What\'s Inside:\\n\\n**Project Showcase:** Dive into the world of open source of KUOSC through detailed project descriptions.Our projects are here to inspire and engage.\\n\\n**Contributors Leaderboard:** Recognizing the dedicated individuals behind our success. The leaderboard highlights top contributors and their valuable contributions.\\n\\n**Knowledge Base:** Whether you\'re a beginner or a seasoned pro, our knowledge base has something for you. Find tutorials, guides, and resources to enhance your skills.\\n\\n**Stay Updated:** Keep track of all KUOSC activities and updates in one place. From events to announcements, you\'ll never miss a beat.\\n\\nJoin us on this exciting journey towards open source innovation. Explore the new KUOSC website today and unlock a world of collaboration and learning. Check it out now at website link!\\n\\nStay tuned for a remarkable open source experience brought to you by KUOSC!"}]}')}}]);